  <brief_title>Preoperative Exercise Test and Postoperative Intensive Care Unit Need in Bariatric Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Preoperative Exercise Test as Predictor for Postoperative Intensive Care Unit Need in Patients Undergoing Bariatric Surgery</official_title>
