  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of our study is to evaluate the efficacy of &quot;60 meters 60 seconds exercise test&quot; (a
      test designed by the study group) done preoperatively as a predictor test for postoperative
      intensive care unit need and extubation success in patients undergoing bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
